description:
When you wish upon a star…💫

Disney is the world’s largest wish granter for Make-A-Wish, granting a wish every hour of every day for children facing critical illnesses.

Disney princesses bring children comfort, hope, and confidence. Each year, thousands of Make-A-Wish kids choose Disney Princesses for their most heartfelt wish.

Learn more at Joy.Disney.com
